        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2018-05-31 11:07:09.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 5:\n\nI have opened a story in JIRA to write unit test for compile-helper-plugin and assigned it to myself. will add automated test for this functionality.\n\nOn the other hand we donot have unit tests written in SDC for components invoked by a framework like Rest service Impl classes, Docker Image creation modules etc. The Maven Mojos fall under similar category and we need a mock provider to test it.\n\nhttps://jira.onap.org/browse/SDC-1392",
        "patchset_number": 5
